            <p class="eyebrow">Service overview</p>
            <h2>What drain repairs actually solves</h2>
            <p>Drain repairs are about restoring flow when cleaning cannot. A separated fitting, a sagging horizontal run, a corroded section, or a bad transition between materials will keep clogging no matter how often the line is snaked.</p><p>Honest Drain inspects the line, prices the repair before any work begins, and protects the work area while the repair is made. Common fixes include replacing a corroded section of cast iron, resetting a kitchen branch with proper slope, and replacing a failed PVC fitting under a sink or in a wall chase.</p>
            <p class="link-row"><a class="text-link" href="../../contact.html">Book a service visit</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="story-card">
            <strong>What this service covers</strong>
            <ul class="pill-list"><li>Section replacement on cast iron</li><li>PVC and ABS branch repairs</li><li>Slope corrections for kitchen and laundry lines</li><li>Trap and tailpiece replacement</li><li>Cleanout installation</li><li>Material transitions done correctly</li></ul>
